{"tid":2230431,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"騰訊員工獲贈華為摺機 部份已在二手網站放售","createTime":"2020-10-05T02:06:27.000Z","updateTime":"2020-10-05T02:10:13.000Z","uid":48083,"like":7,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"031e9c70ffc43144e874b4368adf917da990df9c","tid":2230431,"uid":48083,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-05T02:06:27.000Z","msg":"中國科技巨頭騰訊，早前向平台與內容事業團隊超過 1 萬名員工，每人送出一部華為 Mate Xs 5G 摺機作為中秋節賀禮。華為 Mate Xs 5G 在中國的官方定價為 16,999 人民幣（約 19,400 港元），但由於供應有限，自從 3 月上市後，有網店將之炒至 2 萬人民幣（約 22,825 港元）以上。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/L69FyDe.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FL69FyDe.jpg&h=3f3a6d49&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2020/10/05/100549_63f843d5e46a300e7e78b32572ce6ab2.jpeg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2020%2F10%2F05%2F100549_63f843d5e46a300e7e78b32572ce6ab2.jpeg&h=06185160&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n今次騰訊大手筆找華為定制 Mate Xs 5G 手機，是為了慶祝平台與內容事業團隊成立 2 週年。不過騰訊以華為手機作為中秋禮物，卻成為了員工們套現的好機會，專門售賣二手產品的網站「閑魚」，一下子出現了不少華為 Mate Xs 5G 的放售告示，地點多數是騰訊辦公室所在的深圳、廣東或北京。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://unwire.hk/2020/10/05/tencent-huawei-mate-xs-5g-gift/mobile-phone/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Funwire.hk%2F2020%2F10%2F05%2Ftencent-huawei-mate-xs-5g-gift%2Fmobile-phone%2F&d=A6Q0GQr%2FGmLii1x5qL7rGMpe%2FvQB%2B59L3xQItPRvby0%3D&h=f6a70343\" target=\"_blank\">https://unwire.hk/2020/10/05/tencent-huawei-mate-xs-5g-gift/mobile-phone/</a>"},{"pid":"57482f3bf5f57cc56960bcd7eb7fcf7def593241","tid":2230431,"uid":19552,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-05T02:09:27.000Z","msg":"咁撚貴<img src=\"/assets/faces/cat/sneeze.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1f3acff8d7a3ad51620dc5a2ed856ccfde75c8b1","tid":2230431,"uid":53105,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-05T02:09:29.000Z","msg":"2萬蚊點解唔買fold z 2<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b1052c9de58ce633672833c55fd3f2195d093590","tid":2230431,"uid":2054,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-05T02:10:11.000Z","msg":"2萬買到3部iphone<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/silly.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2acf2d02e4a1ede6a65f10e266c69e9d96eb65e0","tid":2230431,"uid":19552,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"1f3acff8d7a3ad51620dc5a2ed856ccfde75c8b1","tid":2230431,"uid":53105,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-05T02:09:29.000Z","msg":"2萬蚊點解唔買fold z 2<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-05T02:10:13.000Z","msg":"支那人會寧願2萬蚊炒價買IPHONE 12<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}